      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not just one person or anything. it feels like everyone is in on it. even when i'm not on my phone, i feel like people are looking at me differently in the halls or like they're talking about me. it's like there's no version of my life where i'm not the punchline. i feel like i'm just stuck in this loop of being humiliated and i don't see it ever actually stopping.",
